aily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150107%2F18994335&d=ZWeSRS2AzZMtAPOpxiHhOdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=00e72326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150107%2F18994335&h=bf52c700\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150107/18994335</a>"},{"pid":"c8615af653da5a5fa369076177c9e904a59d6d97","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150107/18994335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150107%2F18994335&d=ZWeSRS2AzZMtAPOpxiHhOdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=00e72326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150107%2F18994335&h=bf52c700\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150107/18994335</a></blockquote><br />\n威院內地醫生涉產檢疏忽<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n女嬰四肢嚴重扭曲，年僅一歲半已動過六次手術。家屬提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】威爾斯親王醫院爆出內地交流醫生疑斷錯症事故。年僅一歲半的女嬰出生後確診患上先天多發性關節攣縮症，四肢嚴重扭曲，其母陳太指她懷孕21周時曾於威院做結構性超聲波檢查，負責檢查的內地交流醫生指嬰兒一切正常，質疑對方疏忽不察頑疾，又無按指引將四肢超聲波圖片存檔，她多次向醫管局投訴不果，已向醫委會提出申訴。<br />\n女嬰現於威院兒童深切治療病房留醫，陳太指她懷孕21周時於威院做結構性超聲波檢查，由一名操普通話口音的醫生負責，指胎兒正常，不料女兒出生後證實患先天多發性關節攣縮症、耳積水及裂顎，動過六次手術，一直留院。<br />\n<br />\n「手腳曲成咁都睇唔到？」<br />\n<br />\n她質疑醫生疏忽，「手腳曲成咁，點解會睇唔到？如一早知，唔會俾佢出世受苦」。她屢向醫管局投訴及索取女兒四肢超聲波圖片，但醫院否認出錯，指沒有圖片存檔，只承認涉事醫生屬內地交流醫生。<br />\n立法會議員鄧家彪指院方指引列明需為四肢圖片留檔，批評該院違反守則，又指多個聯網指引均不同，做法混亂。婦產科專科醫生靳嘉仁指，一般結構性超聲波可檢出85%先天性嚴重疾病，但關節問題或較難察覺。威院指涉事孕婦進行檢查時胎兒無異常，結構超聲波檢查不能完全偵測所有缺陷，檢查結果顯示正常，故醫生未將影像存檔。<br />\n■記者鍾雅宜"},{"pid":"d0ee380d3aff43c087998690f68a7babf0526c8a","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150107/18994335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150107%2F18994335&d=ZWeSRS2AzZMtAPOpxiHhOdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=00e72326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150107%2F18994335&h=bf52c700\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150107/18994335</a></blockquote><br />\nthx"},{"pid":"54880634377c6c3489d364cbdf4e5005fc10a6a4","tid":498092,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"選舉近了~<br />\n<br />\n希望樓主唔係熱普城其中一方既支持者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87af49e3044568eca7e7348b61bb5d65c533f1d","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>選舉近了~<br />\n<br />\n希望樓主唔係熱普城其中一方既支持者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我支持獨派。青政。民族黨。學生動源。民族陣線<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">噉你係咪泛民打手?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/145315_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F145315_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=738cc209&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a6fe7f7e438c207f301160e6e1936036cea636c","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>選舉近了~<br />\n<br />\n希望樓主唔係熱普城其中一方既支持者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌鳩楊岳橋賣港就俾泛民打手叫我做熱狗<br />\n我喺另一個post俾另一隻泛民打手叫我做五毛喎<br />\n噉究竟我係五毛定熱狗呀？<br />\n夾撚好口供未呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec37320d658b068fd4eced7f2b4e10d50a101a5","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde768c876198c92ae46d5e90e83fcfeaf1bdd29","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ca8af6fa2f1d0dea1d2bdab370affa77d43a82","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f85a5a184bb76e1c7590ae856cfd3faff2f9f34","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5de67293229f0e7170677bc4661b2806586203d","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96e034ef82bdd4f8cf2b6faaa5f4e210e215c40","tid":498092,"uid":143727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"如果要引入點解只係引入中國而唔係全世界國家既醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就算引入都要佢過到執業試資格，如果唔係香港玩撚密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n引入得不過你要證明你有能力醫人而唔係過黎呃飯食，我覺得要一視同仁，香港讀醫咁難，大陸咁易只要有錢讀書中等都讀到醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人命唔應該政治化同搞自，我都係大陸睇過醫生，好老實咩都用打吊針去醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又被佢醫到喎，不過好濫用抗生素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：政治立場同其視成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b79bb9ab3e68518631f4dae3062595bfdaf2d4","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b07a055a524fbb006babe391d39c8679a195f94","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239e36df3ada9f60326b82e393571b9fa3321c27","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987b28fec92c0196b29c98ad8f163223bf8cdfbb","tid":498092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}